    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-cared for by its previous owner. The exterior retains a strong shine, though you may find a few minor stone chips and light surface scratches upon close inspection. Inside, the cabin is clean and free of major wear, with all electronics and climate controls functioning as intended. It has a complete service history and runs smoothly, making it an excellent choice for someone looking for a dependable, high-quality vehicle without the premium price of a showroom-new model.",
